videos.description: JaVaughn Craig sacked by Tyrell Gilbert for 6  yard loss,  Craig fumbled, recovered by Jaylyin Minor.
videos.headline: Cincinnati forces turnover on strip sack

videos.description: Hayden Moore completes the 16 yard touchdown pass to Thomas Geddis to put Cincinnati on the board first.
videos.headline: Bearcats open scoring with TD pass

videos.description: Hayden Moore finds Kahlil Lewis on the flat who fights off the defender and reaches for the pylon for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Lewis reaches for the Cincinnati touchdown

videos.description: Bryan Wright picks off the pass from JaVaugn Craig near the goal line to end the first half.
videos.headline: Cincinnati ends 1st half with red-zone INT

videos.description: Josh Alexander takes the hand off on the jet sweep and fights his way into the end zone.
videos.headline: Austin Peay scores on jet sweep

videos.description: Mike Boone takes the hand off and rushes for 26 yards and a Cincinnati first down.
videos.headline: Boone rushes for big Bearcat first down

videos.description: Mike Boone going to the ground manages to extend his body into the end zone to score the touchdown for the Bearcats.
videos.headline: Boone reaches across goal line for Cincinnati TD

videos.headline: Breaking down Cincinnati's 26-14 win over Austin Peay
